<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Bosh egib, taʼzim qilay huzuringda Sen Muqaddas,
 Ulugʻlay pok nomingni hayotimda Sen Muqaddas.

[C1]
   Muqaddassan Muqaddas, Xudovandim Muqaddas,
   Muqaddassan Muqaddas, Iso Rabbim Muqaddas.

[V2]
 // Yuvding gunohlarimni Sen pokiza qoning bilan,(2m) //
 // Berib solihligingni aylading bizni muqaddas.(2m) //

[C2]
   Muqaddassan Muqaddas, Xudovandim Muqaddas,
   Muqaddassan Muqaddas, Iso Rabbim Muqaddas.

[V3]
 Muqaddas qoning oqar hamon oʻsha Galgotada,
 Kim tavba qilib borsa aylading uni muqaddas.
 Dunyo rad etsa meni oʻz hatto yaqinlarim ham,
 Ammo rad etmagaysan Sen, chunki sevging muqaddas.

[C3]
   Muqaddassan Muqaddas, Xudovandim Muqaddas,
   Muqaddassan Muqaddas, Iso Rabbim Muqaddas.</lyrics>
<title>Mukaddas Q140</title>
<hymn_number>140</hymn_number>
</song>